{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Review Scope\nCompodoc integration added to Storybook 10.3.5 in an Nx Angular monorepo (ngx-smart-components library). Dev-only tooling, not shipped to production.\n\n## Changes Made\n\n5 commits on branch `uat/phase-5.6-replay`:\n\n1. `990472a` -- Added `\"@compodoc/compodoc\": \"^1.2.1\"` to root `package.json` devDependencies and ran `npm install`.\n\n2. `8b12d3f` -- Flipped `\"compodoc\": false` to `\"compodoc\": true` in both `storybook` and `build-storybook` targets in `packages/ngx-smart-components/project.json`. No `compodocArgs` set; accepts the executor's default `[\"-e\", \"json\"]`.\n\n3. `33a14c7` -- Created `packages/ngx-smart-components/.storybook/tsconfig.doc.json`:\n```json\n{\n  \"extends\": \"./tsconfig.json\",\n  \"include\": [\"../src/**/*.ts\"],\n  \"exclude\": [\"../**/*.spec.ts\", \"../**/*.stories.ts\"]\n}\n```\n\n4. `da22932` -- Created `packages/ngx-smart-components/.storybook/documentation.d.ts` (module declaration so TypeScript resolves the generated JSON import without needing `resolveJsonModule` at bootstrap):\n```typescript\ndeclare module '*/documentation.json' {\n  const value: unknown;\n  export default value;\n}\n```\nAnd populated `packages/ngx-smart-components/.storybook/preview.ts`:\n```typescript\nimport { global } from '@storybook/global';\nimport docJson from '../../../documentation.json';\n\n(global as Record<string, unknown>)['__STORYBOOK_COMPODOC_JSON__'] = docJson;\n```\n(bracket notation required by `noPropertyAccessFromIndexSignature`)\n\n5. `b14763a` -- Added `documentation.json` to `.gitignore`.\n\n## Deviations from Plan\n\n- Plan step 5 (add `resolveJsonModule: true` to `.storybook/tsconfig.json`) was replaced with a `.d.ts` module declaration per advisor recommendation, avoiding a hard compile-time dependency on the generated file.\n\n## Request\n\nVerify the approach is sound and flag any concerns before this is marked complete."}]},"par